        {
            "title": "紅磡電單車「追尾」撞私家車致一傷送院　鐵騎士涉酒駕被捕",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"紅磡電單車「追尾」撞私家車致一傷送院　鐵騎士涉酒駕被捕。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/b9960692c4951aeea53c8fa3462a5e93/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250321/_2025032102273914273.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">紅磡電單車「追尾」撞私家車致一傷送院　鐵騎士涉酒駕被捕。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>紅磡發生酒駕車禍。昨日 （20日）晚上近8時，一輛私家車沿漆咸道北駛至蕪湖街時，因應交通情況收慢，未料遭一輛尾隨電單車撞上。\n\n</p>\n<p>車禍後，私家車上27歲姓陳女乘客感到胸口不適及手痛，由救護車送伊利沙白醫院治理；25歲姓崔男司機則無恙。\n\n</p>\n<p>警員到場調查，為滿身酒氣51歲姓陳男鐵騎士進行酒精呼氣測試，結果超標，遂以涉嫌「酒後駕駛」將其拘捕。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2059385/即時-港聞-紅磡電單車-追尾-撞私家車致一傷送院-鐵騎士涉酒駕被捕",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-21 02:31:11",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "警大埔上水掃黃拘19內地女  年齡介乎28至60歲",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"警大埔上水掃黃拘19內地女  年齡介乎28至60歲。警方圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/0dac4203c46103c0779f3ebc90153745/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250321/_2025032102015539950.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">警大埔上水掃黃拘19內地女  年齡介乎28至60歲。警方圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>大埔警區特別職務隊聯同入境事務處人員，昨日（20日）下午約二時在大埔大埔墟、粉嶺聯和墟及上水石湖墟一帶街道及多個單位展開代號「火石」（FLINTSTONE）的掃黃行動。\n\n</p>\n<p>行動中，人員在大埔寶鄉街、同茂坊、廣福里、上水巡撫街、新財街及符興街的街道上及單位內拘捕共十九名年齡介乎28至60歲的內地女子，涉嫌「違反逗留條件」。所有被捕人現正被扣留調查，稍後將交由相關部門跟進。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4149853/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警大埔上水掃黃拘19內地女  年齡介乎28至60歲。警方圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d2f23d68b15eadd50e4c462f18dc3c74/2025-03/TP_1.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警大埔上水掃黃拘19內地女  年齡介乎28至60歲。警方圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
